paragraphs.context: General Information: We are a rentable boutique studio space that offers workshops in dance, yoga, gym, and more. Our studio operates from 6 AM to 10 PM on all days. We are located at 26, Esi Hospital road, 39/1, 7th Main Rd, HAL 2nd Stage, Doopanahalli, Indiranagar, Bengaluru, Karnataka 560038, India. Workshops: We offer various dance and fitness classes. For details, visit our Instagram page at redbrickstudio_blr. Facilities: Our studio features full-wall mirrors, speakers, air conditioning, a bathroom, a showroom, natural lighting and studio lighting, two spotlights, soundproofing with hollow block construction, and a water dispenser. Age groups: We cater to individuals from beginners to professionals. Max capacity: 30-40 people. Pricing: Our prices are flexible and open to negotiations based on regular usage and days. Weekday rates are 850 INR and weekend rates are 1250 INR. Booking: You can book by calling +91 9880057374, emailing irvincardoza.dev@gmail.com, or sending us a DM on Instagram at redbrickstudio_blr.
